    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span>QMU is to create the next generation of Religious Education teachers by offering a new one-year postgraduate degree which will qualify graduates to work as teachers of Religious, Moral and Philosophical Studies in Scotland’s secondary schools. </span> </p>
<p><span>The University is now accepting applicants for its new PGDE Secondary (Religious, Moral and Philosophical Studies) which will be attractive to graduates who already have undergraduate degrees in a related subject such as religious studies, philosophy, theology, or divinity.</span> </p>]]></Value>
