    <notesToEditors>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span>This course may interest graduates who have degrees covering significant areas of Religious Studies, Philosophy, Theology, Divinity, Sociology of Religion, Anthropology of Religion or Psychology or Religion.</span> </p>
